  "readme_html": "\n        \n          <p><img src=\"https://ollama.com/assets/library/granite-code/e28e37cc-af1b-47d7-bd85-6154b0cf26be\" alt=\"image.png\"/></p>\n\n<p>Granite Code is a family of decoder-only code model designed for code generative tasks (e.g. code generation, code explanation, code fixing, etc.).</p>\n\n<h2>Parameter Sizes</h2>\n\n<ul>\n<li>34B Parameters <code>ollama run granite-code:34b</code></li>\n<li>20B Parameters <code>ollama run granite-code:20b</code></li>\n<li>8B Parameters (with 128K context window) <code>ollama run granite-code:8b</code></li>\n<li>3B Parameters (with 128K context window) <code>ollama run granite-code:3b</code></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Resources</h2>\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/collections/ibm-granite/granite-code-models-6624c5cec322e4c148c8b330\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hugging Face</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2405.04324\" rel=\"nofollow\">Paper</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n        \n      ",
